lead_paragraph: Jordon Ibe came off the bench to drive home the winner as Liverpool took a big step towards reaching the League Cup final with a 1-0 victory at Stoke City in the first leg of their last-four tie on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Advantage Liverpool as Ibe Downs Stoke in League Cup
